\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma_{0}^{-1}=0$
\end_inset

, we get back 
\begin_inset Formula $\cov(\hat{\theta})$
\end_inset

 (i.e.
 like our prior variance goes to 
\begin_inset Formula $\infty$
\end_inset

.
 )
\end_layout

