\begin_inset Formula $\Sigma_{P}$
\end_inset

 is 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

smaller
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 than 
\begin_inset Formula $\cov(\hat{w})$
\end_inset

